description: Returns an array of  SqlInjectionMatchSet objects.

nested_items.name: NextMarker
nested_items.description: If you have more  SqlInjectionMatchSet objects than the number that you specified for Limit in the request, the response includes a NextMarker value. To list more SqlInjectionMatchSet objects, submit another ListSqlInjectionMatchSets request, and specify the NextMarker value from the response in the NextMarker value in the next request.

nested_items.name: SqlInjectionMatchSetId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for a SqlInjectionMatchSet. You use SqlInjectionMatchSetId to get information about a SqlInjectionMatchSet (see  GetSqlInjectionMatchSet), update a SqlInjectionMatchSet (see  UpdateSqlInjectionMatchSet), insert a SqlInjectionMatchSet into a Rule or delete one from a Rule (see  UpdateRule), and delete a SqlInjectionMatchSet from AWS WAF (see  DeleteSqlInjectionMatchSet).

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the SqlInjectionMatchSet, if any, specified by Id.
